method CREATEIXMLDOCFROMOBJECT.
*/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
*|   This file is part of the SAPlink-plugins.                         |
*|                                                                     |
*|   The code of this project is provided to you under the current     |
*|   version of the SAP Code Exchange Terms of Use. You can find the   |
